snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator | Halloween House Seasonal Trailer
snippet.description:
It's time for a spooky clean!
Prepare yourselves for a chilling new Halloween House Seasonal job for to PowerWash Simulator. 
Help Muckingham's local witch to clean up ready for the Halloween party of the year! 
The Halloween House Seasonal is out now, available to play for free on PC, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PlayStation 4|5 and Nintendo Switch.
 #powerwashsimulator
◆Official Website: https://www.square-enix.com/asia/newsportal/
◆Official Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SquareEnixAsia/
